Took me a while to get to sleep last night, but I slept through on half a Z till 05:15. Took my morning codeine and meditated until about 07:00.

Starting at about midday yesterday, my mood started to improve. Had a nice long rest after doing the Body Scan at 13:00 and my ankle didn't disturb me. Ended up having some nice shared activity on Facebook in the afternoon and playing backgammon on my phone till about 19:00.

&nbsp;

To bed at 18:18. Fell asleep fine. Woke at 02:40 and after a while took some bits of Zopiclone. (I'd been trying unsuccessfully to cut quarters with the new pill shape, so must have taken about half a Z.) On reflection, taking it that late made me feel quite groggy, so will try without. Awake just after 6, up at 08:30 for my weekly Skype with Sarah &amp; Jamie. Out to collect my prescription. Sarah said she was feeling a bit flat today and I feel the same. A persistent sensation of having done something wrong. Of having made a mistake that will cause me to suffer retribution.

On the domestic front, have repotted my maidenhair fern and cooked fish and chips for lunch. I bought that Russell Hobbs iron yesterday and ironed a couple of hankies. It's nice to use a proper iron again.

